# Styling

- Use Tailwind CSS with design tokens from `globals.css` (`primary`, `secondary`, `brand-blue`, `brand-orange`).
- Brand colors: blue `#1a4683`, orange `#f58432` — use CSS variables, never hardcode in components.
- No inline styles. Use `cn()` for conditional classes.

```tsx
// ❌ BAD
<button style={{ backgroundColor: "#1a4683" }} />

// ✅ GOOD
<Button variant="default" />
```
